ose.<\/p>\n<p>Six $5,000 scholarships are provided by G3 Grow Beyond to high school students with innovative ideas for the development of Canadian agriculture in the future. For a chance to win, submit a video describing your vision.<\/p>\n<div id=\"ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_trProvidedBy\" class=\"Column4Layout Right-Column\">\n<h2 id=\"summary\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Summary\"><\/span><strong>Summary:<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Provided by:\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 <a href=\"https:\/\/www.g3growbeyond.org\/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">G3<\/a><\/p>\n<p>Renewable:\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 No<\/p>\n<p>Scholarships Available:\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 6<\/p>\n<p>Type of Award:\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 Contest<\/p>\n<p>Automatic Consideration:\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0No<\/p>\n<p>Application Deadline:\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 26 April, 2024<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<h2 id=\"eligibility-requirements\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Eligibility_Requirements\"><\/span><strong>Eligibility Requirements:<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong>Level of Study<\/strong>:\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 Diploma; Bachelor;<\/p>\n<p><strong>Gender<\/strong>:\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 \u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 Any<\/p>\n<p><strong>Year of Study:\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 <\/strong>Entering first year<\/p>\n<p><strong>Citizenship:\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 <\/strong>Canada<\/p>\n<p><strong>Status in Canada:\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 \u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 <\/strong>Permanent Resident<\/p>\n<p><strong>Schools Attended\u201d\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 <\/strong>Any School<\/p>\n<p><strong>School of Study:\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 \u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 <\/strong>Any School<\/p>\n<p><strong>Field of Study:\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 <\/strong>Any Field of Study<\/p>\n<p><strong>Region of Residence<\/strong>:\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 Canada<\/p>\n<p><strong>Course Load:\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 <\/strong>Full-time<\/p>\n<p><strong>Region of Study:\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 \u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 <\/strong>Canada<\/p>\n<p><strong>Activities:\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 \u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 <\/strong>N\/S<\/p>\n<p><strong>Financial Need:\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 <\/strong>No<\/p>\n<h3 id=\"requirements\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Requirements\"><\/span><b>Requirements<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Create a 1-2 minute video describing your vision for the future of agriculture.<\/li>\n<li>Log in, apply, and submit your video by April 26, 2024, at 11:59 PM CST.<\/li>\n<li>Submit all accompanying documents as outlined. Post-secondary acceptance letters must be received by June 16, 2024.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 id=\"assessment\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Assessment\"><\/span><b>Assessment<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>1) How well your video addresses the questions below. This will be judged by a panel of industry professionals. (65%)<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>What is your chosen field of study and why does it interest you?<\/li>\n<li>What is one major challenge facing the world that you believe could be addressed through innovation in the field of agriculture?<\/li>\n<li>Describe this innovation and how your studies can achieve it.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>2) Online public voting. A maximum of one video vote (per IP address) will be allowed for each of the five geographic regions designated on the website. (25%)<br \/>\n3) Community and\/or school involvement. (10%)<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"contact-information\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Contact_Information\"><\/span>Contact Information<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>G3 Grow Beyond Scholarship<\/p>\n<p>+1-204-983-0239<\/p>\n<p>200 Portage Avenue, 3rd Floor, Winnipeg, MB, Canada. R3C 3X2<\/p>\n<h3 id=\"apply-now\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Apply_Now\"><\/span>Apply Now<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.g3growbeyond.org\/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Click Here<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"To meet global demand, the agriculture sector&#8217;s future depends on technology and innovation. You are the only hope&hellip;\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":353,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[14],"tags":[28],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/351"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=351"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/351\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/353"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=351"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=351"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=351"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}